title: Morgan2 Gets Strange Dating App Request + Bobby The Historian: Origins Behind Famous Sayings + TV Shows We’ve Abandoned
itunes:title: Morgan2 Gets Strange Dating App Request + Bobby The Historian: Origins Behind Famous Sayings + TV Shows We’ve Abandoned
description:
Morgan2 got an interesting message on a dating app that she wanted to share with the show. A group of guys had an interesting proposition for her and she wanted to know if it's a good idea. Bobby reveals the famous origin stories behind sayings we all use in everyday life. Plus, we all share TV shows we started, but never went back and finished!
